##
## Introduction
##
@node Introduction "Introduction"

    This small program emulates a CPC 6128 on our dear machine, the AMIGA.
    Why a CPC emulator ? Because this machine helped me to discover
    data processing, assembly programming, demos... 

    This program is surely not perfect (I am a beginner on AMIGA...), so,
    I accept (and recommand) every remarks to ameliorate it.

    This version is freely distribuable.

    Of course, I would be very happy if you would send me everything that
    works on AMIGA : hardware (why not...), some public domain programs,
    mods, pics (I prefer the JPEG format), but do whatever you want...

@endnode


##
## Warning
##
@node Warning  "WARNING"

    This program is far from being perfect, and it can subsist some small
    "bugs". Also, you can use this program at your own risks; anyway, I
    could not be held responsible problems caused by the utilization of 
    this software on your machine.

@endnode


##
## Copyrights
##
